(121, 1, '2016-02-24 15:27:18', '2016-02-24 12:27:18', 'Obtained information from large databases, helps to solve actual business problems. Often it is the unstructured data with non-standard file structures or formats that are difficult to manage.  It also requires a permanent high-speed access to the data.\r\n\r\nWe will help to create an IT infrastructure that will support the processing of large amounts of data. Our solutions for big data services include the development of strategies, planning, protection and implementation.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>What we do:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>strategic architecture</li>\r\n	<li>highly productive platform for maintaining strategic architectures</li>\r\n	<li>platform integration</li>\r\n	<li>backup systems</li>\r\n	<li>big data protection</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Big Data', 'Obtained information from large databases, helps to solve actual business problems. Often it is the unstructured data with non-standard file structures or formats that are difficult to manage.  It also requires a permanent high-speed access to the data.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '24-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-24 15:27:18', '2016-02-24 12:27:18', '', 24, 'http://localhost/inity/2016/02/24/24-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(122, 1, '2016-02-24 15:44:15', '2016-02-24 12:44:15', 'Our specialists have years of experience in software development for the automation of work processes in areas such as telecommunications, finance, industry, and others. At the start of the project we study the client''s company, identify problematic points and offer possible remedies. For the reorganization of business processes we use all our available expertise, we take into account the specifics of the areas in which the client works, and long-term goals of the company. At the next stage, our team is developing a package of recommendations and automation to improve the situation in the company and, if necessary, creates a business system from a scratch.\r\n\r\nOur aim in each case is to help the company to achieve the required level of performance, which will result in the growth of the company''s profits and brand awareness.\r\n\r\n<strong>What we do:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>audit</li>\r\n	<li>legal consulting</li>\r\n	<li>check for quality standards compliance</li>\r\n	<li>focus groups</li>\r\n	<li>automation solutions</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nnetwork programming', 'Business process automation', 'Our specialists have years of experience in software development for the automation of work processes in areas such as telecommunications, finance, industry, and others. At the start of the project we study the client''s company, identify problematic points and offer possible remedies.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '26-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-24 15:44:15', '2016-02-24 12:44:15', '', 26, 'http://localhost/inity/2016/02/24/26-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(123, 1, '2016-02-24 15:44:39', '2016-02-24 12:44:39', 'We offer solutions for the implementation of cloud solutions to help your business reduce costs, improve the security of IT services and enable rapid scaling of IT resources. After studying the situation, we will select the best cloud solution for your company and carry out full or partial migration of IT services to the cloud.', 'Cloud Solutions', 'We offer solutions for the implementation of cloud solutions to help your business reduce costs, improve the security of IT services and enable rapid scaling of IT resources.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '22-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-24 15:44:39', '2016-02-24 12:44:39', '', 22, 'http://localhost/inity/2016/02/24/22-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(124, 1, '2016-02-24 15:45:10', '2016-02-24 12:45:10', '<strong>FINclub</strong>\r\n\r\nFINclub platform - is the online service for microcredit. With its help, investors and borrowers can communicate with each other quickly and without excessive bureaucracy to take or to lend money via the Internet.\r\n\r\nWe have developed a software that allows support staff easily monitor all financial and administrative processes. And FINclub users can post a request to examine and to compare the proposal, to lend money or to borrow. Provided for this purpose:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>three-tier verification during the registration</li>\r\n	<li>database of proposals from investors and their terms of lending</li>\r\n	<li>the protection system of personal information</li>\r\n	<li>online wallet</li>\r\n	<li>user-friendly personal cabinet interface</li>\r\n	<li>the opportunity of the fast implementation of investments and loans</li>\r\n	<li>opportunity to choose the loan amount, purpose, and duration</li>\r\n	<li>verification of compliance with the loan pre-specified criteria</li>\r\n	<li>the possibility of resale of the loan</li>\r\n	<li>accounts statistics</li>\r\n	<li>control of the security of financial transactions</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Financial products', 'FINclub platform - is the online service for microcredit. With its help, investors and borrowers can communicate with each other quickly and without excessive bureaucracy to take or to lend money via the Internet.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-24 15:45:10', '2016-02-24 12:45:10', '', 16, 'http://localhost/inity/2016/02/24/16-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(125, 1, '2016-02-24 15:45:38', '2016-02-24 12:45:38', 'Our solution in the bank systems sector allows us to regulate operations, increase the efficiency of work and as a result - increase profitability and business performance. We help to implement an innovative and strategic business solution for internet acquiring systems, which are characterized by high complexity due to the constant data exchange and interaction with a foreign software and hardware complex.\r\n\r\n<strong>What we do:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>audit and consulting</li>\r\n	<li>standards compliance and requirements of regulatory authorities</li>\r\n	<li>big databases</li>\r\n	<li>real-time analytics access</li>\r\n	<li>multifactorial authentication</li>\r\n	<li>optimized interfaces</li>\r\n	<li>secure access to business applications</li>\r\n	<li>technical support</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Financial systems', 'Our solution in the bank systems sector allows us to regulate operations, increase the efficiency of work and as a result - increase profitability and business performance. ', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-24 15:45:38', '2016-02-24 12:45:38', '', 14, 'http://localhost/inity/2016/02/24/14-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
