(139, 1, '2016-02-25 12:17:11', '2016-02-25 09:17:11', 'Our designers do an excellent job with difficult tasks of designing intricate services, make all the confusing user interfaces easier and more convenient, and with its extensive experience in UX / UI, help to create adaptive systems, which will improve the conversion and, therefore, increase sales. Every online project must consider the user preferences. Therefore, we will test the product, study users’ behavior, and analyze the objectives to be achieved in the final result.\r\n\r\n<strong>What we do:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>static and dynamic websites prototypes</li>\r\n	<li>user-centered design</li>\r\n	<li>UX/UI analysis and testing</li>\r\n	<li>study of user behavior scenarios</li>\r\n	<li>focus groups and reporting</li>\r\n</ul>', 'UX/UI', 'Our designers do an excellent job with difficult tasks of designing intricate services, make all the confusing user interfaces easier and more convenient...', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '46-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-25 12:17:11', '2016-02-25 09:17:11', '', 46, 'http://localhost/inity/2016/02/25/46-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
